room_title: Escape room "Yin Yang" by Escape Room Missouri City in Houston
room_description:
Imagine you’re dropped into a world where everything is black and white. You feel like you’re Alice in Wonderland where nothing seems as it should. How can you escape this world, when all the puzzles and clues have no clear solutions and your team bickers with each other?
It’s up to you to unite the players by merging their Yin and Yang personalities into a perfect whole. If you don’t, then you are stuck in a world where there is no color. Can you bring the best traits out of each player to escape the room?
